laughing jackass
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:<i>Sceloglaux albifacies </i>, a SI nocturnal bird, phs named by Australian-bred settlers, to be distinguished from morepork and from the little owl; =laughing owl, =whekau. also contrast jackass-bird.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
